<item>
            <title>[LU-17550] direct IO does not return ENODATA on crossover to empty layout</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17550</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a write crosses from an area of a file with a layout to one without, the write should return ENODATA.&#160; Due to layout caching in the direct IO path, we need an extra check for this to work correctly for DIO.&lt;/p&gt;

